snippet.title: The Well - Trailer | Turtle Rock Studios
snippet.description:
Debut trailer for The Well, a fantastical RPG for Gear VR developed by Turtle Rock Studios. This video provides a look at some of the gameplay brave adventurers will experience on October 11.

More info at: 
Oculus Page → trs.gg/TheWellVR
Website → http://TheWellVR.com
Turtle Rock Forums → https://talk.turtlerockstudios.com
